concept.description:
Labels all classes annotated with @jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.ConversationScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped or a stereotype
            annotation with "CDI", "JEE" and "Injectable".

Labels all types of fields annotated with @jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.ConversationScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped or a stereotype
            annotation with "CDI", "JEE" and "Injectable".

Labels all return types of methods annotated with @jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped,
            @jakarta.enterprise.context.ConversationScoped, @jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped or a stereotype
            annotation with "CDI", "JEE" and "Injectable".
